  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YtDraMh.jpg\" alt=\"BIome Bundle\" width=\"1903\" height=\"761\" /><br /><br />BiomeBundle is a preset for OpenTerrainGenerator</strong> originally created by MCpitman. </span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">It is a completely<strong> custom world pack&nbsp;</strong>containing<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;400+ original biomes with over 2000 structures </strong></span>including custom trees, rocks, caves, dungeons, villages and much more.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Original BiomeBundle was created for <strong>1.10-1.12 OTG version</strong> and he is really <strong>broken in 1.16</strong> OTG version.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>BiomeBundleReloaded is the new 1.16 BiomeBundle,</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>It need OTG 1.16 to work&nbsp;which must be downloaded separately <a title=\"here\" href=\"https://www.openterraingenerator.org/otg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a></strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"LC20lb MBeuO DKV0Md\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🔨<a title=\"INSTALLATION\" href=\"https://openterraingen.fandom.com/wiki/Installing_Presets\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">INSTALLATION</a></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"LC20lb MBeuO DKV0Md\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">📷<a title=\"BIOME BUNDLE SCREENSHOT\" href=\"https://imgur.com/a/yFdyv\">BIOME BUNDLE SCREENSHOT</a>&nbsp;</span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"LC20lb MBeuO DKV0Md\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">💬<a title=\"DISCORD\" href=\"https://discord.gg/ncVTPztKJc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">DISCORD</a></span></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">It took me so much time to bring this up... i really love Biome Bundle .&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If you enjoy it like me and want it to be maintained please consider donating.</span></p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: 34px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a title=\"DONATION BUTTON\" href=\"https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=ZMNZCXPMAVECY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">DONATION BUTTON</a></span></h4>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
